<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ gěi wǒ de tài duō 迦南254</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ gěi wǒ de tài duō wǒ gěi zhǔ de tài shǎo
 cǐ shí wǒ fǔ fú zài zhǔ miàn qián wèi yǔ lèi xiān luò
 wǒ de líng cháo bài nǐ zài yī cì lián mǐn wǒ
 chéng wèi shèng jié de ér nǚ zài zhǔ lǐ miàn huó
 zhǔ de líng gǎn dòng wǒ gǔ zhōng shì hū yǒu shāo zhe de huǒ
 yǎn jīng bù néng tíng liú zài cǐ kè hái yǒu xīn de bá shè.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>254</hymn_number>
</song>